{"type": "article", "id": 27340, "title": "仿穿山甲的背包", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-26T06:58:38Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 70, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702171457EmBuAgHzSJ39bTnp.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>第一眼看到这些层层叠叠的黑色“盔甲”时，你可能还以为这是来自科幻电影的概念。实际上这是 Pangolin 以穿山甲（也就是品牌名所指的动物）为灵感，采用“半机械半野兽”的仿生设计理念推出的一款皮革背包。Born 除了有着帅气的外型，内部空间也非常充足，不仅有可以放置 iPad 的夹层还有能够收纳小物件的拉链口袋。如果你对它感兴趣的话可以通过<a href=\"http://pangolin.com.co/collections/born\">链接</a>购买，价格根据背包大小从 490 至 580 美元不等。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171455sgcwF37R6A9dIWSB.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702171456axYMoSw3nHBjDdeg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021714566GZ9Emu7T3BMN0Kd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021714572PlYxkinFJObKcsQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}